{"tid":852393,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"IG女神既初戀係毒丁","createTime":"2018-10-07T22:52:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T08:44:24.000Z","uid":195041,"like":3,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6aa626302378a00191b4592a1eccd5924e5963e5","tid":852393,"uid":195041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T22:52:18.000Z","msg":"我21歲<br />\n琴晚冇啦啦諗起一個中一既同桌女仔<br />\n於是就睇番佢既fb wall <br />\n<br />\n呢個女仔當年寫過情書比我，因為嗰陣我冇鍾意過佢而且人生第一次收情書有嗰種不知所措<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 既感覺 所以收到情書之後我冇任何表示<br />\n係佢寫完情書我冇任何回應既之後持續一年，佢喺wall不斷抒發對呢件事既少女傷感情懷，因為印象中個陣好似收情書之後完全冇理過佢  而家諗翻起都覺得內疚<br />\n<br />\n我講翻我背景先<br />\n印象中既自己係細個到初中好sporty 成績唔錯兼識氹女仔既男仔 算係班入面既風頭人物 所以先吸引到故事中既女主角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係不知曾幾何時我已經從一個外向好動既男仔慢慢變成一個內向既人，到而家連朋友都好少既毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講翻琴晚重溫完佢個wall突然之間諗起一路以嚟都冇睇過佢ig 點知一睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢已經唔再喺嗰種mk相或者偽韓相，佢po嗰d 係模特兒嗰種相!! 想入面既佢非常之有氣質而且帶有自信...配埋佢初中個陣po文都已經有既文采caption <br />\n<br />\n睇完之後我第一時間諗起既唔係而家咁索既女神點解當初冇答應同佢一齊 而係諗翻自己由花花公子變成真毒撚 大學生活唔參加活動 上fb ig齋做CD rom既廢人 而中一果嗰向我寫情書既弱質少女而家變成好有自信 ig幾千個follower 生活多姿多彩既真女神嗰種極大反差!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我已經差佢幾皮 啱啱仲幻想如果我地兩個再相遇，佢見到我而家仲係梳緊中小學生留陰髮型 同埋一身既毒撚裝扮 佢一定會諗 我以前竟然會愛過呢一個死毒撚 一笑置之<br />\n<br />\n好啦文就打完 其實主要都係想抒發吓睇到佢嗰一刻既心情"},{"pid":"1310d478e5f20c57d78176a95dde8b28b2d1ee24","tid":852393,"uid":195041,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T22:57:06.000Z","msg":"而家對住佢d相打緊飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89bbc6794ebf074451ab6f100ab2ab9d05c9987e","tid":852393,"uid":195041,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T22:58:59.000Z","msg":"一嚟就負評<br />\n究竟有冇人理解我嗰種複雜心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5773b78d68e40ad62c9b0d3e205fd2f09e4d69f5","tid":852393,"uid":12514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1310d478e5f20c57d78176a95dde8b28b2d1ee24","tid":852393,"uid":195041,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T22:57:06.000Z","msg":"而家對住佢d相打緊飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T22:59:17.000Z","msg":"0<span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span>"},{"pid":"40f896b95cc4f494b71087ed88c2b6a116a8c52f","tid":852393,"uid":195041,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5773b78d68e40ad62c9b0d3e205fd2f09e4d69f5","tid":852393,"uid":12514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1310d478e5f20c57d78176a95dde8b28b2d1ee24","tid":852393,"uid":195041,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T22:57:06.000Z","msg":"而家對住佢d相打緊飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T22:59:17.000Z","msg":"0<span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T23:00:07.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"56141f0184ccaf7b07c163420ba7c97b4872d90c","tid":852393,"uid":208442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T23:03:13.000Z","msg":"Princejoyce?"},{"pid":"440c6aa81c26b4af564a9d70c24892a4be57090f","tid":852393,"uid"